---
title: Caramelized Shallot Risotto with Zucchini Ribbons
description: Balsamic-roasted shallots are folded into a creamy risotto for a truly luscious meal. We’ve added gorgeous zucchini ribbons for color and a bright squeeze of lemon. Now, cancel that reservation and serve this on Valentine’s Day instead!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54c908a76ced6e5f178b456a.jpg
